com.esri.mo2.sys.tp
Interface ThreadPoolListener

All Superinterfaces:
EventListener
public interface ThreadPoolListener
extends EventListener

This interface supports objects that require notification of ThreadPoolEvents.

A threadpool event occurs when the size of the ThreadPool is altered, or when a Task is begun/stopped.

See Also:
ThreadPoolEvent, ThreadPool
